articles.author: Sporting News
articles.title: Liverpool exhorté à recruter Kane après l'humiliation face à Man City - Goal.com
articles.description: Ole Gunnar Solskjaer has defended the performance of Donny van de Beek in the FA Cup win over West Ham after Mark Hughes suggested that the Dutchman's slow start to life at the club is down to a lack of trust from his team-mates.
